description: Chuck is a cyborg thug stalking the wastelands of a ravaged earth trying to forget his past; a past filled with torture, demon pumpkins, and a red-haired girl he will never see again. But when a psychotic man-child and his bionic tiger threaten humanity's last hope for survival, Chuck must decide if he is a hero - or a blockhead. You will learn the answer as well in this riotous lampoon of the funny pages set after the Apocalypse! This omnibus collects over ten years of Jason Yungbluth's Weapon Brown comic series and includes new stories, pin-ups, annotations and more!

ALL-NEW DIGITAL-EXCLUSIVE CHAPTER!

See the worlds outside the Weir for the first time, as Alice and her new allies take an epic journey to lay their fallen comrade to rest - in the smouldering caldera of a huge volcano!

An ending and an epic new beginning, all in one!

(Note, this all-new chapter is included in the Weirding Willows Vol. 1 Collected Edition, and is a digital-exclusive bonus issue for those readers picking up the series in single issues)

For centuries, the dark lord Rainier has set his sights on mastering the world's science and technology in order to bring about his rise to power, yet now he's realized the error in his ways. As Rainier attempts to regain his connection to magic, he may be able to regain everything that was once lost to him!
